{"tid":2081331,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謊報18年！「前AV教主」蒼井空曝真實年紀…連生日都騙","createTime":"2020-06-27T06:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T07:41:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48ffcd383a123309f8324099341243c8bc1264a8","tid":2081331,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"日本前AV女優蒼井空外型甜美、身材火辣，退出AV界後結婚生子，去年5月更為老公DJ NON剖腹誕下一對雙胞胎，組織幸福家庭，出道18年的她，剛推出小說式自傳《夜過黎明後 蒼井空》，書中自爆其實自己出道以來都謊報年齡，真實年齡已經39歲了，並非資料上的36歲。<br />\n<br />\n蒼井空2002年進入暗黑圈拍片，當時對外公開的資料為1983年11月11日東京出生，在書中提到，其實實際年齡少報了3歲，現在的自己，已經39歲了，並非資料上的36歲，生日也不是11月11日。<br />\n<br />\n蒼井空表示因為AV女優的身份，不想個人資料曝光，所以使用藝名及虛構出生日期，出生地點也非東京，而是神奈川的鄉下地，不過她也已經把每年「雙11」當成自己生日，希望粉絲亦繼續如此，「我不打算更改它」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.setn.com/news/768708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F768708&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=a83c1bb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F768708&h=786ed65a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.setn.com/news/768708</a>"},{"pid":"fdcc1ee24bd422c030c3a803c5cdc336781dfed7","tid":2081331,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/27/2630369-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2F2630369-XXL.jpg&h=38207274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本前AV女優蒼井空當媽後以顧小孩為樂。（圖／翻攝自臉書）"},{"pid":"a89c60867819e5a10883b7832f72134723b1b264","tid":2081331,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cf89b95eaff2469985280b00a4ca7c4956c412","tid":2081331,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score